2025-11-28PSPCNational Capital ActOrder Approving that the NCC Extend the Lease with Ottawa Riverkeeper Inc. Order approving that the National Capital Commission grant one option to extend the lease with Ottawa Riverkeeper Inc., for a period of five years, beginning on March 1, 2028, 2033, 2038, and 2043 respectively, for a portion of the club level (floor 1) and a portion of the 3rd level of the real property located at 501 Sir George Etienne Cartier Parkway, in Ottawa, Ontario.N/A
subject: Order Approving that the NCC Extend the Lease with Ottawa Riverkeeper Inc.
precis: Order approving that the National Capital Commission grant one option to extend the lease with Ottawa Riverkeeper Inc., for a period of five years, beginning on March 1, 2028, 2033, 2038, and 2043 respectively, for a portion of the club level (floor 1) and a portion of the 3rd level of the real property located at 501 Sir George Etienne Cartier Parkway, in Ottawa, Ontario.
